## Appendix B: Interaction Patterns Reference
 
### Desktop Hover Interactions
 
| Pattern | Implementation | Effect |
|:---|:---|:---|
| **Card hover** | `hover:border-brand-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-50/50 transition-all` | Border turns gold, shadow lifts with warm tint |
| **Icon container hover** | `group-hover:bg-brand-50 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors` | Neutral → gold tint |
| **CTA reveal** | `opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity` | Text fades in on card hover |
| **Arrow nudge** | `group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform` | Arrow slides right 4px |
| **Coin photo hover** | `group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform` | Subtle zoom |
| **Underline** | `decoration-brand-200 group-hover:decoration-brand-600 transition-all` | Underline intensifies |
| **Shadow lift** | `shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow` | Card elevates |
 
### Mobile Touch Interactions
 
| Pattern | Implementation | Effect |
|:---|:---|:---|
| **Button press** | `active:scale-95` | Shrinks on press |
| **Nav link press** | `active:scale-[0.98]` | Subtle compression |
| **Touch targets** | Minimum `w-11 h-11` (44×44px) | Accessibility guideline |
| **Backdrop dismiss** | Full-screen overlay, tap to close | Standard drawer pattern |
 
