## Appendix C: Design Decisions Log
 
| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|:---|:---|:---|
| Separate API server | Express.js, not Next.js API routes | Serves both web and mobile. Clean separation of concerns. No vendor lock-in. Independently scalable. |
| PostgreSQL over NoSQL | Prisma + PostgreSQL | Relational data (users → coins → evaluations). ACID transactions for payment operations. Free and open source. |
| Razorpay over Stripe | Razorpay | Strong UPI/India support. Client preference. Competitive pricing. Good mobile SDK. |
| React Native (Expo) | Over Flutter | Shared TypeScript/React knowledge with website. Camera/gallery built into Expo. Same Zod validation schemas. Single language across all platforms. |
| JWT over Sessions | JWT access + refresh | Stateless API serving both web and mobile clients. Refresh token rotation for security. Works with mobile app without cookie complexity. |
| Admin assigns experts | Not auto-assignment | Client requirement. Admin knows expert availability, expertise depth, and workload. Simpler to implement correctly. Can add auto-suggest later. |
| Heritage Gold palette | Over Nordic Blue (VägVisaren) | Coins are gold, bronze, copper, silver — the palette should reflect the subject matter. Gold conveys premium and trust. Heritage feel for a numismatic audience. |
| Monorepo | Over separate repos | Shared types package (`@mintmarks/shared`). Single PR for cross-cutting changes. Unified CI/CD pipeline. Turborepo for parallel builds. |
| Email + in-app notifications | Over push notifications (v1) | Simpler architecture. No FCM/APNs setup required. Push notifications deferred to v2 when user base justifies the complexity. |
| i18n-ready, English-only launch | Full next-intl architecture from day 1 | Adding Hindi, Spanish, or any language is just adding a translation JSON file. No architectural changes needed later. |
| Playfair Display + Inter | Font pairing | Playfair = editorial authority (museum catalogs, auction houses). Inter = screen-optimized readability for dense data. Together they signal "expert but accessible." |
| UUID primary keys | Over auto-increment integers | Prevents ID enumeration attacks. No information leak about entity count or creation order. Required for a system handling payment data. |
| Abstract storage interface | Pluggable S3/Cloudinary/local | Client wants to decide image storage provider later. Interface-based design means swapping is a config change, not a code rewrite. |
 
